  "body": "#### System information\n\nUbuntu 14.04 Linux 64bit.\n\nGeth version: 1.4.5\nOS & Version: Linux\n#### Expected behaviour\n\ntestnet usually consumes around 5KB/sec for both up and download\n#### Actual behaviour\n\nWhen connecting to certain peers upload is shooting up to maximum upload bandwith\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\n\nWatch your network stats\n\nI have blocked these peers with firewall rules, but it would great to whitelist peer versions via config or CLI args.\n",
